This means `v_p = w_p + Σ c_i (PreInternalTangentSpace.lof p w₁ - PreInternalTangentSpace.lof q w₂)`.
This doesn't immediately give `v_p = w_p`.

But if `v_p - w_p ∈ Submodule.span ℝ S`, then `v_p - w_p` is in the subspace.
So `v_p = w_p` in `PreInternalTangentSpace x`.

Let's try to prove this directly.

